<div class="side-card wall-card">
<div class="card-icon">🧱</div>
<h3 class="wall-title">The Wall</h3>
<p class="card-description">Current AI agent systems are built by engineers for engineers, creating massive consumer friction.</p>
<ul class="feature-list">
